    "stem": "A country grain elevator has a cash inventory of 10,000 bushels bought October 1 at $4.00 per bushel. The cash position was hedged in the December future with a 10 cents-per-month full carrying charge. The position is closed out December 1, when December futures and cash are both at $4.00. What is the net gain or loss per bushel on the combined futures and cash positions?",
