    "stem": "Your customer is long 10 August (front month) crude oil futures and short 10 December crude futures (back month) on the NYMEX (each contract is 1,000 barrels). The spread at the beginning is +1.75; on offset of the positions, it is -1.50. What is the profit or loss?",
